To run Scipyen the following requirements must be met:
    
    Python 3.9.+ installed on the local machine.
    
    A python virtual environment:
        On Linux: use virtualenv
        On windows & macOS: use mambaforge

Further requirements:
MacOS: a rust compiler is needed to build safetensors, needed by torch (from linguistics)
	to install, get it from https://rustup.rs


	
    

    
    
    
